1.0 DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES
The Employee뭩 duties and responsibilities as Warehouse Planner includes:
 Coordinate with customers &amp; hauliers (truckers) for cargoes to be packed into or unpacked from the containers.
 Input Data Entry
 Checking of shipping documents to ensure cargoes are of the correct size and volume to be packed into the size of the containers.
 To liaise with customers via e-mail or phone calls for any disputes on volume and size of cargo, if any.
 To confirm and receive the correct cargoes from transporters when required
 To perform physical checking of cargoes and attending to surveys requested by customers.
 To ensure special requests by the customer pertaining to the containers are complied
 To assist on other area as and when required.